title: Service Fabric Yeoman Generators
body:
Service Fabric Yeoman Generators for project scaffolding:

**Java Applications:**
https://github.com/Azure/generator-azuresfjava
- Java Reliable Services and Actors templates

**C# Applications:**
https://github.com/Azure/generator-azuresfcsharp
- .NET Core service templates

**Guest Executables:**
https://github.com/Azure/generator-azuresfguest
- Packaging existing applications

**Container Applications:**
https://github.com/Azure/generator-azuresfcontainer
- Docker container service templates

These generators help bootstrap Service Fabric applications with proper project structure and configuration files.
